HEADWORD: Oversoul
<hw>O"ver*soul`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The all-containing
soul.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>That unity, that <qex>oversoul</qex>, within which every man's
particular being is contained and made one with all other.</q>
<rj><qau>Emerson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Oversow</ent>⟦br⟧
